flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-n4-sdk: Proof/evidence flow shows how a claim becomes checkable."]
    N2["2. Claim: This unit performed: Encode API requests | Handle bridge/proof models | Return typed results."]
    N3["3. Witness or input: developer app | gateway endpoint | wallet/config"]
    N4["4. Execution or check: validate config, encoded result, signing policy, and target response"]
    N5["5. Public commitment: request digest, network profile, and output artifact hash"]
    N6["6. Verifier: apps | operators | integration tests"]
    N7["7. Accepted result: typed client result | transaction request | query response"]
    N8["8. Rejected result: return diagnostics; do not sign, submit, or publish"]
    N1 --> N2
    N2 --> N3
    N3 --> N4
    N4 --> N5
    N5 --> N6
    N6 --> N7
    N7 --> N8
